channel.title: Others can connect but I cannot...?
channel.description:
First before I begin This isn't a moparscape question, as I am not apart of that community...
Ok I have a Linksys router but when i look up my default gateway it shows my modems gateway.. so I use my modems gateway and it acts as a router in a way its a Westell router well after i set up my shit how its suppose to be, every other person can connect but I cannot whys this?
